data.description: Take a swing at a comfortable lifestyle in the Ryder. Move easily and contentedly throughout your domain, first stopping at your home office to drop off a file then making your way into the welcoming kitchen. Busy hands and lots of laughs make short work of dinner preparations. Once dinner is out of the way, it's time for homework ? either at desks in the upstairs bedrooms or the homework center you built in the game room. Parents can unwind in the cozy primary suite. With no floor overhead, you'll never hear the pitter patter of little feet.
